description:
The Bible is clear about what marriage is and who and what it’s for. It is a matter of unity, intimacy, and spirituality, and it is a beautiful gift from the God of Creation. #Shorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ #YouTubeShorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ 

Listen to Pastor Ted Wilson’s message about biblical marriage and what the Bible teaches.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oJ2894XguvI&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo_ANrUJhHN2_4bSlMDTjuqQ&index=40
